apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: dependency-workflow-23-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: getuserid
        template: getuserid
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: username
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.username }}'
      - name: playlistname2id
        template: playlistname2id
        dependencies:
        - getuserid
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: playlist_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.playlist_name }}'
      - name: addsongtoplaylist
        template: addsongtoplaylist
        dependencies:
        - playlistname2id
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: user_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.getuserid.result }}'
          - name: playlist_ID
            value: '{{ tasks.playlistname2id.result }}'
          - name: song_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.song_name }}'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: movie-ticket-booking-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: getshowtimes
        template: getshowtimes
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: movie_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
          - name: city
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.city }}'
      - name: booktickets
        template: booktickets
        dependencies:
        - getshowtimes
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: movie_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
          - name: showtime
            value: '{{ tasks.getshowtimes.result }}'
          - name: number_of_tickets
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.number_of_tickets }}'
  templates:
  - name: getshowtimes
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
      - name: city
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/movieshowtimes"
      method: "GET"
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
      - name: city
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.city }}'
  - name: booktickets
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
      - name: showtime
      - name: number_of_tickets
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/booktickets"
      method: "POST"
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}'
      - name: showtime
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.showtime }}'
      - name: number_of_tickets
        value: '{{ inputs.parameters.number_of_tickets }}'
